RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT BRANCH_CODE, BRANCH_NAME FROM OLTMS_BRANCH WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH UNION SELECT 'ALL','ALL BRANCHES' FROM DUAL
SELECT RATE_CODE ,RATE_CODE_DESC FROM LFTMS_STANDARD_RATE_CODE UNION SELECT 'ALL','ALL RATE CODES'FROM DUAL ORDER BY RATE_CODE
SELECT CCY_CODE ,CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE RECORD_STAT ='O' AND AUTH_STAT='A' ORDER BY CCY_CODE
